    dc:description "FIGURE 1: Gaeolaelaps carabidophilus Trach n. sp.: A – idiosoma, dorsal view; B-D – variety of shape of epigynal shields; E – tectum; F – subcapitulum and palp; G – movable digit of chelicerae; H – fixed digit of chelicerae. Scale bar: A-D 200 µm, E-H 100 µm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4639912/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

